flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens Baram]) --> ConnectWallet{Wallet Connected?}

    ConnectWallet -->|No| ShowLock[Show Lock Screen]
    ShowLock --> ConnectMethod{Connection Method}
    ConnectMethod -->|Google| ZkLogin[zkLogin]
    ConnectMethod -->|Password| SelfCustody[Self-Custody Wallet]
    ZkLogin --> WalletReady
    SelfCustody --> WalletReady

    ConnectWallet -->|Yes| WalletReady[Wallet Ready]
    WalletReady --> LoadHistory[Load Encrypted Chat History]
    LoadHistory --> ChatUI[Chat Interface]

    ChatUI --> SelectModel[Select AI Model]
    SelectModel --> TypePrompt[Type Prompt]
    TypePrompt --> Submit[Submit]

    Submit --> AutoAssign[Auto-Assign Executor]
    AutoAssign --> FetchPubKey[Fetch Executor RSA Public Key]
    FetchPubKey --> Encrypt[RSA-OAEP Encrypt Prompt]
    Encrypt --> BuildTx[Build On-Chain Transaction]
    BuildTx --> SignTx[Sign Transaction]
    SignTx --> SubmitTx[Submit to Nasun Blockchain]

    SubmitTx --> EscrowCreated[NUSDC Locked in Escrow]
    EscrowCreated --> CallExecutor[Send Encrypted Prompt to TEE]
    CallExecutor --> WaitResult[Waiting for TEE Execution]

    WaitResult --> ResultOk{Success?}
    ResultOk -->|Yes| ShowResult[Display AI Response]
    ResultOk -->|No| ReRoll{Re-Roll Available?}
    ReRoll -->|Yes| AutoAssign
    ReRoll -->|No| ShowError[Display Error]

    ShowResult --> SaveChat[Save to Encrypted IndexedDB]
    SaveChat --> ChatUI

    style AutoAssign fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style Encrypt fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0
    style EscrowCreated fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100
    style ShowResult fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
